rows.label: tlk43200143_01_msg0002
rows.name:
My parents are gone too,
but I'd never considered
harboring a grudge...

rows.label: tlk43200143_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I mean, revenge doesn't actually
solve anything, and it's not like
he can bring them back.

rows.label: tlk43200143_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Ah, well, life here is fun enough for me.
No point in making a fuss, really.
